snippet.textDisplay:
Again same old fusion rock, western, sufi, filmy songs??? Going to be redundant! And hold on.. is there going to be Rap(e) too? :-(

Still missing lot of good talented singers (non-filmy) and regional classical music.

Except ARR and few other handful of performances rest of Coke Studio India has been a disaster mainly due to bad music arrangement and lack of fresh attempts.

With all the social media and communication medium, these guys can find the raw talent or alteast give a chance for the singers from Saregamapa shows. This is the reason for downfall of Indian music!
